
**Better pattern** (graph-native, single query):
```cypher
MATCH (ku:Knowledge {uid: $uid})

// Fetch prerequisites
OPTIONAL MATCH (ku)-[r1:REQUIRES_THEORETICAL_UNDERSTANDING|REQUIRES_PRACTICAL_APPLICATION]->(prereq)
WHERE coalesce(r1.confidence, 1.0) >= 0.7

// Fetch dependents
OPTIONAL MATCH (ku)<-[r2:REQUIRES_THEORETICAL_UNDERSTANDING|REQUIRES_PRACTICAL_APPLICATION]-(dependent)
WHERE coalesce(r2.confidence, 1.0) >= 0.7

// Fetch extensions
OPTIONAL MATCH (ku)-[r3:EXTENDS_PATTERN|DEEPENS_UNDERSTANDING]->(extension)

// Fetch simplifications
OPTIONAL MATCH (ku)<-[r4:SIMPLIFIES]-(simpler)

RETURN
    ku,
    collect(DISTINCT {uid: prereq.uid, title: prereq.title, confidence: r1.confidence}) as prerequisites,
    collect(DISTINCT {uid: dependent.uid, title: dependent.title, confidence: r2.confidence}) as dependents,
    collect(DISTINCT {uid: extension.uid, title: extension.title}) as extensions,
    collect(DISTINCT {uid: simpler.uid, title: simpler.title}) as simplifications
```

